    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Summary</h2><strong><i>&quot;Heeey! Park-Boy!&quot;</i></strong> is a simple game I made about watering flowers, spreading joy and rebuilding things that were once broken.<br><br>It was heavily inspired by the games like &quot;Chibi-Robo: Park Patrol&quot; and &quot;Katamari Damacy&quot; - two of my favourite games.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864750/extras/e17d3db80945f3c164ab15afb380573e.poster.avif?t=1642248871\" width=492 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864750/extras/e17d3db80945f3c164ab15afb380573e.webm?t=1642248871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864750/extras/e17d3db80945f3c164ab15afb380573e.mp4?t=1642248871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2>In the game, you play as Yuu-Boy - an alien that has crash-landed in an old city park.<br><br>His ship ran out of fuel (which of course, is happiness) and now he is stuck. <br><br>You have no choice but to try and spread love as much as you can to try and get Yuu-Boy home!<br><br>You do this, at first, by watering flowers - but over time you unlock the ability to redecorate the park with items you buy.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864750/extras/2fd79236f0fc088d5162b68ef64a4089.poster.avif?t=1642248871\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864750/extras/2fd79236f0fc088d5162b68ef64a4089.webm?t=1642248871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864750/extras/2fd79236f0fc088d5162b68ef64a4089.mp4?t=1642248871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Water flowers and make them dance.<br></li><li>Buy and sell objects for your park and decorate it however you like.<br></li><li>Unlock tools and upgrades for Yuu-Boy.</li></ul><br>I hope you enjoy my game!",
